{
  "stem": "10698.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the gate to come in-- there was-- it was so wide, that you could, several trucks, going in and out at the same time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They opened all the-- the gates, and we started-- some on all four, because they let us know that the soldiers are coming-- and we went out to greet the American soldiers.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we dropped to their feet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we kissed their boots.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were some of them that couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were just crawling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They picked up and carried the men into the camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if you-- and if-- and if Hollywood would put something like that, they would say oh, God, another Hollywood thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But this is something that stays so much in me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "First of all, the first thing that they did is spray us with DDT-- which is outlawed now-- because we were with lice-- head lice, clothes lice.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were-- they were eating us up alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Every time we killed a-- excuse me-- a louse, it was full of blood.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then they started to give us food, and a lot of people died.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because their-- they couldn't-- their system couldn't take it anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were watching-- we were like five-- and we're watching one another not to overeat-- we would watch one another to eat within limits, because a lot of people died.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I had a woman that walked next to me-- well, I was a young kid then.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She was a middle-aged woman, and she said, oh, God, I would like to live once more to eat a decent meal.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't care if I die.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She had her wish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I saw her die after she ate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They didn't realize in the beginning, right in the beginning, not to give us all that food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
